"SoiBoshi|\n"
"|5|![](mn05.png)|Сердце|&sigma; Sco|NakagoBoshi|\n"
"|6|![](mn06.png)|Хвост|&mu; Sco|AshitareBoshi|\n"
"|7|![](mn07.png)|Корзина|&gamma; Sgr; иногда &eta; Sgr|MiBoshi|\n"
"\n"
